There is something special when creative people get together. Being inexhaustible, life and nature are a constant stimulus for a creative mind. It is the supreme art of the teacher to awaken joy in creative expression and knowledge.

Unique Approach

To create something exceptional, your mindset must be relentlessly focused on the smallest detail. The creation of something new is not accomplished by the intellect but by the play instinct acting from inner necessity. The creative mind plays with the objects it loves. Being inexhaustible, life and nature are a constant stimulus for a creative mind.

Create The Best

It is the supreme art of the teacher to awaken joy in creative expression and knowledge. The uncreative mind can spot wrong answers, but it takes a very creative mind to spot wrong questions.

item.title: Measuring Tape
item.content:encoded: Tape Measure makes it easy for one person to make measurements and markings, thanks to its rigidity and a positive blade lock to keep it unspooled. The metal tape has a 7 ft. standout and features 16 in. and 19.2 in. stud-center markings for framing purposes, while a Mylar polyester film protects the design. Built for fluid retraction, this rugged, metal-constructed tape measure resists corrosion for lasting durability.

item.title: Wall Spatula Scraper
item.content:encoded: Wall scraper is a great tool for handling many surface preparation jobs. It comes with a nylon handle which cleans up easily and will slide in and out of your pocket quickly. It has a 3-inch wide stiff blade ideal for scraping. Taper ground, mirror polished carbon steel blade. Solvent-proof, classic nylon handle. Dual rivet construction. Always wear eye protection.

item.title: Wall Paint Roller
item.content:encoded: Roll up and down, from floor to ceiling and move over about three-quarters of a roller width each time so you’re always slightly overlapping the previous stroke. When you reach the corner, roll as close as you can to the adjacent wall without touching it. Repeat Steps 1 through 3 until the entire wall is painted.

item.title: Pneumatic Hand Drills
item.content:encoded: A pneumatic tool, air tool, air-powered tool or pneumatic-powered tool is a type of power tool, driven by compressed air, supplied by an air compressor. Pneumatic tools can also be driven by compressed carbon dioxide (CO2) stored in small cylinders allowing for portability.

item.title: Measuring Instrument
item.content:encoded: A tape measure or measuring tape is a flexible ruler. It consists of a ribbon of cloth, plastic, fiber glass, or metal strip with linear-measurement markings. It is a common measuring tool. Its design allows for a measure of great length to be easily carried in pocket or toolkit and permits one to measure around curves or corners.

item.title: Concrete Cutter
item.content:encoded: Electric Angle Cutter with 14 in. Diamond Blade (4114X) is a powerful concrete cutting solution engineered for a range of applications, especially ideal for edge-to-edge cuts. Powered by a 15 Amp motor with 3500 RPM for the most demanding jobs, the cutter offers versatility with a removable base for closer edge-to-edge cuts and an adjustable tool base that allows for up to a 5 in. cutting depth

item.title: Hand Saw
item.content:encoded: Wood-Handled Aggressive-Tooth Saw features hardened teeth with a tri-bevel design to tackle the toughest cutting jobs. The large handle size is designed to help lessen fatigue when cutting. Constructed of precision ground and set teeth for smooth and accurate cutting.

item.title: Head Protection Helmet
item.content:encoded: It is better not to crash at all, then to crash wearing a helmet. But if you do crash, a helmet works to absorb the force, which protects your head, which in turn protects your brain. Helmets work to prevent head injuries which becomes even more important for children whose brains are still developing.
